              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "EN-RSL-FW"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The incident energy 5.0 MeV, the neutron",
                " energy spread was 25 keV, mainly due to the proton",
                " energy loss in the gas cell and the finite angle",
                " subtended at the target by the scattering sample"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".Produced by pouring molten pure Na metal (> 99.5% Na,",
                " remainder mostly O2), in an argon atmosphere, into",
                " a light cylindrical Al can of wall thickness 0.04 cm.",
                ".The enclosed Na sample was 4.5 cm diam., 4.6 cm long",
                " and weighed 71.093 g and was X-rayed to confirm the",
                " absence of voids."
              ]
            }
          ],
